---| \`default\` | int | Sets default parameters for the RadioFX DSP and enables it. |
---| \`freq_low\` | float |  |
---| \`freq_hi\` | float |  |
---| \`fudge\` | float |  |
---| \`rm_mod_freq\` | float |  |
---| \`rm_mix\` | float |  |
---| \`o_freq_lo\` | float |  |
---| \`o_freq_hi\` | float |  |
